JOHANNESBURG, South Africa, March 7, 2022/APO Group/ --
                                                        
                            21,020 tests were conducted in the last 24hrs, with 801 new cases, representing a 5.5% positivity rate. Today @HealthZA  reports 62 deaths; of which 6 occurred in the past 24–48 hours. Total fatalities are 99,609 to date.